                <div class="middle"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/view/page_note/large/public/p34234963-1.jpg" alt=""><br><span class="pic-title"></span></div>
越来越觉得每个哲学家的观念都是相通的啊。是不约而同还是受影响呢
